to be treated as humans.

552
00:40:59,623 --> 00:41:01,208
How about that?

553
00:41:01,292 --> 00:41:02,835
Is he about to get caught?

554
00:41:02,918 --> 00:41:04,170
Goodness!

555
00:41:04,879 --> 00:41:06,505
