556
00:41:06,589 --> 00:41:08,716
They need to be taught a lesson.

557
00:41:08,799 --> 00:41:10,759
-Honey!
-What are you…

558
00:41:11,343 --> 00:41:12,470
doing right now?

559
00:41:12,553 --> 00:41:15,055
